title: How To Combat Imposter Syndrome and live an integrated life
description:
Have you ever felt LIKE an imposter in a space you belong in? Chelsea and Judah discuss the phenomenon known as Imposter Syndrome and talk about moments in their lives when they've felt out-of-place. Plus, they also share the "Two I's" to combat Imposter Syndrome.
